Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.40,0:01:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,笑笑嘛  薰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:01.86,Comment,,0,0,0,,舞衣  想吃什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.30,0:01:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.29,0:01:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,穿浴衣花了點時間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.63,0:01:09.40,Comment,,0,0,0,,真熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我們也才剛來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.49,0:01:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,姬和果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,穿浴衣很合身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.83,0:01:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,日本的浴衣雖然很美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.44,0:01:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,唯獨胸部很難受這點不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,姬和  走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.82,0:01:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,被困在這種地方  和我一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(683,658)}撈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,至少把你們救起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不過我是不會得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,薰好像很開心  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.32,0:01:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的  沙耶香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.66,0:01:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,薰明天開始又要去遠征了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.18,0:01:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,薰  我也來一起撈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.27,0:01:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,姬和  是烤玉米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,這就買來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.52,0:01:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這些你都嚐過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,味道都怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:01:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這破獎品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要是我認真起來用刀一招就秒殺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不能用刀的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  美炎她們在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.57,0:02:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,說是有任務來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:04.72,Comment,,0,0,0,,刀使炒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,做炒麵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,作為回饋本地的一環
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.20,0:02:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我們調查隊要在廟會上擺攤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  不是小荒魂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟現在社會上刀使的風評不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:19.52,Comment,,0,0,0,,這是為了改善形象
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:21.99,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b0\fs28\frz23.69\c&HF6DCD4&\pos(548,518)}FROM:山城由依
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是煙火大會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都穿浴衣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,來張照片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這輩子就靠這個活下去了!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.92,0:02:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不傳給我就死給你看!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.24,0:02:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,傳給我!!浴衣!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.60,0:02:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,對了  我們裡面誰會煮飯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我只會炒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我會給食材分類和秤重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.98,0:02:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我會吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.05,0:02:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,這個味道不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是團隊協作的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是我以前提議的特訓的成果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.32,0:02:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.39,0:02:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好  繼續炒起來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.40,0:03:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,客人太多啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,對味道的期待50%
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.36,0:03:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,對刀使的興趣20%
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.79,0:03:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,少女做的炒麵的誘惑60%
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.22,0:03:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,有志者…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.62,0:03:08.48,Comment,,0,0,0,,還沒好?  快點  肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.82,0:03:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,好像成不了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,去和大家會合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.65,0:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.43,0:03:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回平城了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以…
